{
    "type": "Recipe",
    "title": "Installing the toolchain",
    "tool": "darwin_deps-0.9.3",
    "platforms": { "platform": "darwin" },
    "description": [
        "Complete the following steps to install the Zephyr requirements and the GNU ARM Embedded Toolchain on macOS.",
        "For more information, see [Development Environment Setup on macOS](https://developer.nordicsemi.com/nRF_Connect_SDK/doc/0.3.0/zephyr/getting_started/installation_mac.html) in Zephyrâ€™s Getting Started Guide."
